{
  "texts": [
    "The process consists of 3 steps: sampling, prompt designing, and deployment.",
    "The sampling step involves defining the task and collecting data and annotations.",
    "The prompt designing step involves creating and refining prompts using different types and language models.",
    "The deployment step involves selecting the best model and deploying the model for clinical use.",
    "LLM: large language model; NER: named entity recognition; NLP: natural language processing; RE: relation extraction."
  ]
}